{"tid":218464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叻叻林鄭特首用2000蚊聘請公司取消FB 戶口","createTime":"2017-04-26T13:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T14:09:44.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9b7b71228b2374f296aef1854252177213cd76","tid":218464,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"林太競選時開設facebook專頁同網民「connect」，單喺1月26日至2月26日一個月，佢已經花費最少30萬元管理專頁。林太亦另外申報2000蚊開支，聘請公司喺下年3月幫佢取消（cancellation）facebook帳戶、YouTube帳戶同競選網頁。 <br />\n<br />\n林太2月初喺會展舉行一場星光熠熠嘅造勢大會，吸引數百位城中政商巨頭撐場，呢場分享會花費逾113萬元，佢同助選團當時著住特別訂製嘅藍色T恤登場，當中有27件T恤每件價錢約555元，總數1.5萬元，而發票特別註明呢27件T恤係「Reproduction of T-shirt（From Reconnect to Weconnect）」，未知係咪買方或賣方出錯後需要重製T恤。 - <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170426/s00001/1493212630890#sthash.dX0p1OLW.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170426%2Fs00001%2F1493212630890%23sthash.dX0p1OLW.dpuf&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4ca8ac8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170426%2Fs00001%2F1493212630890%23sthash.dX0p1OLW.dpuf&h=c12d6d74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170426/s00001/1493212630890#sthash.dX0p1OLW.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"760aceead5098a0c7724420876aa78dd7e81ea5f","tid":218464,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"冇人想知"},{"pid":"a7e1762c182383e0aaf24ed2423eecea088c4e84","tid":218464,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"有27件T恤每件價錢約555元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908dc4993daae2f863825619300ceac19a2d7682","tid":218464,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply